ource/Television_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All times BST  From 8am: Women's golf  The women's golf action kicks off in Paris this morning following the conclusion of a thrilling men's competition on Sunday.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 866, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.771185251522265e-22, \"text\": \"BST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\"}, {\"begin\": 932, \"end\": 937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.955707777618091e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a dramatic finale at Le Golf National, withScottie Scheffler just pipping Britain's Tommy Fleetwood to goldafter a nightmare for Jon Rahm.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1166, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"score\": 0.999999999614829, \"rank\": 3.853463781073793e-10, \"text\": \"Scheffler\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\"}, {\"begin\": 1102, \"end\": 1109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999033484575, \"rank\": 9.665165689351902e-08, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1112, \"end\": 1127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Fleetwood\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tommy Fleetwood\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Fleetwood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Fleetwood\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We should be in for more drama over the next few days, with reigning world No1 Nelly Korda the favourite.\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1247, \"end\": 1258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nelly_Korda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nelly Korda\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nelly_Korda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nelly_Korda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"GB's Charley Hull will hope to add an Olympic medal to her two LPGA Tour wins, but admits she could be impacted by a smoking ban on the course.\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1274, \"end\": 1276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999990671430882, \"rank\": 9.328576939174766e-07, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1279, \"end\": 1291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charley_Hull\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charley Hull\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charley_Hull\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charley_Hull\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From 12:52pm - Cycling team pursuit  It's been a successful start for Team GB in the Velodrome, with a phenomenal gold in the women's team sprint followed by themen's sprint team claiming an impressive silveron Tuesday.\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1638, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now the respective team pursuiters will be looking to follow suit, with the men's lineup of Ethan Hayter, Ollie