ud joins Enhanced Games  Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year  Keely Hodgkinson reveals Grand Slam Track decision and 2025 ambitions  Make 2026 the year of working smarter  He has cruised into the men's 400m final, with the Wolverhampton star now looking to add an Olympic medal to his 2023 World Championship silver.\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2349, \"end\": 2365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2510, \"end\": 2523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wolverhampton_Wanderers_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999920178197, \"rank\": 7.982250200752184e-09, \"text\": \"Wolverhampton\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wolverhampton_Wanderers_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wolverhampton_Wanderers_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"06:30:Athletics- Marathon Race Walk Relay Mixed  11.13:Sailing- Women's Dinghy Medal Race  11:54:Climbing- Women's Speed Final  12:13Sailing- Men's Dinghy Medal Race  13:43:Sailing- Mixed Multihull Medal Race  14:00:Weightlifting- Men's 61kg  14:43-Sailing- Mixed Dinghy Medal Race  16:30:Skateboarding- Men's Park Final  17:04:Cycling track- Men's Team Pursuit, Finals  17:15:Athletics- Women's Pole Vault Final  17:15:Wrestling- Champ-de-Mars Arena Mat B  17:57:Cycling Track- Women's Team Pursuit, Finals  18:30:Artistic Swimming- Team Acrobatic Routine  18:30:Weightlifting- Women's 49kg  19:19:Taekwondo- Women's 49kg Bronze Medal Contests  19:25:Athletics- Men's Discus Throw Final  19:34:Taekwondo- Men's 58kg Bronze Medal Contests  20:19:Taekwondo- Women's 49kg Gold Medal Contest  20:20:Athletics- Men's 400m Final  20:30:Boxing- Women's 57kg